                "description": {
                    "chat": "",
                    "unidentified": "",
                    "value": "<p>The attic whisperer siphons the breath from living creatures, sapping their strength. A living creature hit by a jaws Strike must attempt a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-traits=\"curse,incapacitation,necromancy,occult\" data-pf2-label=\"Steal Breath DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 24 hours and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fatigued]{Fatigued}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is enfeebled 1 for 24 hours, is fatigued, and falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious}.</p>"
                },
